    <a id="materials"><h3>Materials</h3></a>
    <p>
      <span>
        <strong>OX:</strong> Our oxidized finish is a special treatment of our sterling silver that gives it a blackened surface. This surface finish wears off over time with the friction against the skin, revealing the silver underneath to create a silvery-black patina.
         </p><p>
        <strong>Brass:</strong> We use brass that comes from refinery that is certified as green.
         </p><p>
        <strong>Kohl:</strong> Our Kohl finish is a nickle-free ruthenium black plating. It is more permanent than oxidation and has a matte gunmetal look. This is used in our rings and pieces that are intended to stay black over time.
         </p><p>
        <strong>Vermeil:</strong> We use a heavy 14kt gold plating that is 3 times as thick as common gold plating.
        14kt/18kt Yellow, Rose, Green or White gold. All of our gold is made using 100% recycled.
         </p><p>
        <strong>Please Note:</strong> Vanessa Lianne Jewelry is all hand made using recycled metals and conflict free stones
      </span>
    </p>
